summary:
In March 2018, I succesfully finished my Maritime Security Operative course at the European Security Acadamy in Poland. Now, I am looking for a position as a Martime Security Operator onboard of a vessel.
 
I have worked as a Legionair in the French Foreign Legion for the past 2,5 years, including a mission in French Guyana. Besides this, I have worked as a deckhand on a commercial vessel on international canals. I am 23 years old but the maritime security sector is where I wish to make my carreer. I’m hard working, eager to learn, loyal and disciplined.
I speak Dutch, English and French.
I am available immediately and I am currently based in the Netherlands, ready to commence employment.
